Initialize Bivvy configuration for a project

Usage: bivvy init [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -c, --config <CONFIG>      Path to config file (overrides default .bivvy/config.yml)
      --minimal              Generate minimal config without prompts
  -p, --project <PROJECT>    Path to project root (overrides current directory)
      --template <TEMPLATE>  Start from a specific template
      --from <FROM>          Copy configuration from another project
  -v, --verbose              Show verbose output
      --force                Overwrite existing configuration
  -q, --quiet                Minimal output
      --no-color             Disable colored output
      --debug                Enable debug logging
      --trust                Trust all remote extends URLs without prompting
  -h, --help                 Print help
  -V, --version              Print version
